2. IDENTIFIERS ➖
—-------------------------
Identifiers is nothing but name given to the java components ( classname, variable name, method name).

IDENTIFIER RULES ➖
—-----------------------------
Identifier should not start with number
Identifier can contain numbers
Keywords is not allowed
Special symbols is not allowed except _, $.

