IT RULES FOR CLASSNAME ➖
—------------------------------------------
Classname should start with uppercase
If class name contains more than one word each and every word of first letter should be uppercase
\IDENTIFIER RULES FOR VARIABLENAME & METHOD ➖
—--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Variable name/ methodname should start with lowercase
If variablename / method name contains more than one word  first letter should be lowercase and second word of the first letter should be uppercase

